I am a former Marine, Recon to be exact. Alot of the fellow Marines that were training us, etc. Were Vietnam Vets, they would explain the reasoning behind the motives that they were teaching us. That made a great impact onto my life and how i conduct it. My Uncle was the reason i joined the Corps, he was Recon in Vietnam, from the beginning to almost the end. I was never there but I have the DEEPEST respect for all those who served. I would love to repond with any who would like to respond to me.<br><br>
Semper Fi...<br>

